I’ve identified a concrete gap to address: we currently emit many atomic section slots, but not a compact deterministic section-style slot that captures the combined structure (numeric vs suffixed, suffix kind/case, and trailing punctuation). I’m adding that composite style emission in both decompiler slot output and F-logic component output, plus regression tests.
